Four Wire Fire Alarm Project
----------------------------

Project Description: This is the project which is designed for protecting the buildings against fire
			It is a alarm system to avoid the fire. There is base board and Floor board
			for each floor.

Files		:Program Folder: Base Board Program
		 Slave Program Folder : Floor board Program
		Schematics : Base and Floor Board Schematics
		Simulation: Simulation for the system

Project Author : Raghavendra Chandra Ganiga

Project Code	: Hotty Thinker
